            <div class="title">
                House Of Commons (Rebuilding)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1945-01-25/debates/3e42ad5d-111e-4b37-8448-bb86127cf161/ConsolidatedFund(No2)Bill" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
