<p class="">I think the hon. Gentleman is labouring under a misapprehension in suggesting that there is greater accommodation on the Floor of this Chamber than there was on the old one. In fact, there is exactly the same accommodation, and the width between the walls is identical.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
