            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-d1e03e4c-507e-4dd3-9da3-1f1684ea68e5" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
