<p class="">May I interrupt my hon. and gallant Friend? I find, on looking at my copy of the Report, that there is clearly shown upon drawing No. 9, a clock, or what is intended by the architect to be a clockface, over Mr. Speaker's Chair.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
