<p class="">If a public competition were to be held, would that not increase, by a great many months, if not years, the time needed for a decision to be reached?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f44103a6-0f5e-4e1c-91bc-568b9973ccfc" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
