        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-54ea599c-f45e-4036-b7ec-d107d6c2540f">
                Sir Herbert Williams  (Croydon, South)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-54ea599c-f45e-4036-b7ec-d107d6c2540f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1945-01-25/debates/be7b0d23-c59d-47b7-b3ae-95d2a1b8080e/HouseOfCommons(Rebuilding)#contribution-54ea599c-f45e-4036-b7ec-d107d6c2540f">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">May I ask the hon. Member what speed he wants to give the House of Commons?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
